                            Sanitation Supply System Credit (KSPAMS). Bank Kalimantan Barat also introduced the Drinking
                            Water and Sanitation Credit (KREASI). Beyond banks, cooperatives such as Sangosay in NTT,
                            along with Credit Union Keling Kumang and Lantang Tipo in West Kalimantan, also joined the
                            network.</p>
